{
  "stem": "23572.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I remember one time, without knowing it, all of a sudden, I see-- myself-- I see German soldiers marching.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Unbeknown to me and another friend, we had-- we-- we went back in the German-- the German part.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we said to ourselves there that the best thing to was just be quiet.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, we-- we just walked like we were farmer boys and went back to the Italian part.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the German soldiers didn't-- didn't even pay any attention to us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they were just marching there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They weren't-- weren't on guard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But, you know, out in the fields, you just walk, and all of a sudden, you're in German territory.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I forgot that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I was lucky.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Anyhow, so that's-- that's our life up in Lesno Brdo.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And eventually-- eventually, we had to almost ask the Italian army to evacuate us from there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was getting too dangerous for us to be there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] there was shooting back and forth between the Italian army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We were in the middle, and we were kids.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we really asked the Italian army to-- to-- to get us out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Now, these are things which people have told me because I was not involved in the negotiations.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I just-- And eventually, the Italians made us civilian prisoners of war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "That's what they [? called us. ?] We practically-- and they-- they sent us to central Italy, in a little village called Nonantola.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Nonantola is in the province of Modena.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "A Jewish fellow, at one time, owned this big villa.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But it was abandoned.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And now, through the Jewish, the Italian Jewish community, somehow we were able to get this place so that the-- the Italians would send us to this particular village.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
